 Restaurant. We take special care of every aspect of guest services and experience and a feedback is very important to us. We provide you a great ambience in our lodge and give you a beautiful experience whether in business or a personal stay. The lodge offers a great ambience and well equipped with efficient service with a personal touch. Our Accommodation units are spacious and uniquely designed with elegant interiors to make one feel cozy and enjoy blissful bedroom comforts.',NULL,NULL,12,'http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445822.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445820.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445790.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445792.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445794.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445800.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445804.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445810.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445812.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445814.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445816.jpg|http://stay-imgs.stayzilla.com/resize/1200x800/80180/445818.jpg',NULL,NULL,25.3091545,83.0019836,'1 Adult 1 Kid','https://www.stayzilla.com/stays/ganga-tourist-lodge-80180?checkInDate=04-08-2016&checkOutDate=05-08-2016&source=propertyCard','Ramapura Luxa, Varanasi',80180,'Ganga Tourist Lodge','Lodge','2016-07-20 12:10:45 +0000','2016-07-20 12:10:45 +0000','830per night incl. tax','Single Non-A/C Rooms',NULL,'Not Verified','Tiwari Guest House|Hotel Natraj|Shanthi Guest House|Hotel Star Palace','www.stayzilla.com',NULL,'Kindly Note:|Lodge doesnt have restaurant in the premises but kitchen available.|This tariff is not applicable for long weekends, government holidays and festival period.','a8b7792b5f09c67f942321d9c543e443');
